  "keyFeatures": [
    "Unified implementations of 10+ Linear RNN architectures (S4, S5, LRU, Mamba, etc.)",
    "Custom CUDA kernels for optimized training and inference performance",
    "Multiple API levels: scan operations, recurrent steps, and full layer implementations",
    "Support for both Linear Time-Invariant (LTI) and Linear Time-Varying (LTV) models",
    "Pre-built architectures for language modeling, U-Net, and hierarchical classification",
    "CUDA graphs-based inference with 10x speedup over naive implementations"
